  "intro": "<p>My original plan for this day was to go the 60+ miles to the <a href=\"www.thehiddenspringsinn.com\">Hidden\n\t\t\t\t\t\tSprings Inn</a> which would have left Monday a 90 mile day into Silver City. I was concerned about the\n\t\t\t\t\t\tweather in the afternoon so I left before 6am. For the first time on the trip I had made a reservation in\n\t\t\t\t\t\tadvance to stay at this inn.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>",
