  "content": "<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Quamado to Reserve</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel1\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"0\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic01.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                          class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Sunrise heading south from Quamado</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>1</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic02.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n                                                   class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>xxxx</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>2</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic03.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                   class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>xxxx</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>3</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic04.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                   class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>xxxx</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>4</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel1\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel1\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                        <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                        </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>The first real place to stop was in Reserve after 53 miles. The first 23 miles was a gradual climb up to\n\t\t\t\t\t\t8,000 feet and then it was downhill into Reserve which was back down at 5,800 feet. There was a store and\n\t\t\t\t\t\trestaurant and I bought some snacks but decided to head up to the hotel which was about 7 miles away.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic05.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Nice house along the way\n                            </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>I arrived at the Hidden Springs Inn before noon but the wind from the south had already picked up. I went\n\t\t\t\t\t\tinto The Adobe Cafe and Bakery which was part of the hotel and had a great smoothie. I almost couldn't\n\t\t\t\t\t\tfinish it because of the brain freeze. I cancelled my reservation and decided to fight the wind another 30\n\t\t\t\t\t\tmiles and see what was in Glenwood, the next town south. All the people in the cafe assured me \"it's\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdownhill from here\".</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic06.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Gila National Forest and the CD off to the east.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic07.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Gila National Forest and the CD off to the east.\n                            </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic08.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Heading south on US Route 180\n                            </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>The first 7 miles from the Hiden Springs Inn was a nice downhill and then there was a three mile climb\n\t\t\t\t\t\tbefore I finally did have a nice downhill into Glenwood.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic09.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Last ridges before my \"coast\".\n                            </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Glenwood, NM</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Glenwood had two or three motels and I stayed at <a href=\"www.whitewatermotel.com\">the Whitewater Motel</a>which\n\t\t\t\t\t\twas next to the Whitewater Creek which because of all the rain seemed to have some water in it.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel2\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"4\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic10.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                                  class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Afternoon rain in Glenwood</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>1</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic11.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Afternoon rain in Glenwood</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>2</p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic12.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Happy I'm not in it</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>3</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic13.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Afternoon rain in Glenwood</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>4</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic14.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Ice backs and a nicce place to sit.</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>5</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel2\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel2\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                        <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                        </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.row -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.container -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>I had a porch out front and after making a few phone calls sitting at the post office next door I got some\n\t\t\t\t\t\tice for my knees and some food from the store down the street and spent the afternoon nice and dry. The rain\n\t\t\t\t\t\treally came down about 4 o'clock but let up in time for me to go to the Golden Girls Cafe down the\n\t\t\t\t\t\tstreet.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container-fluid\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6.col-lg-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t        src=\"https://api.smugmug.com/services/embed/4256885064_9H2QFxc?width=960&height=540&albumId=51125178&albumKey=Z2x9Wr\"></iframe>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<hr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- \t.col-lg-12 -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.row -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.container -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"../img/tourdivide/day34/day34pic15.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\"><a href=\"www.whitewatermotel.com\">The Whitewater Motel</a></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Golden Girls Cafe was only open from 4pm to 7pm on Sundays. I had a nice beef brisket dinner and some pie\n\t\t\t\t\t\tfor desert. Nice end to a very good day with only 60 miles to Silver City and then another 80+ miles to the\n\t\t\t\t\t\tMexican Border.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Ain't no stopping me now</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Text by <a href=\"http://www.havingadventures.com/\">Jim O'Brien</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t. Photographs by Jim O'Brien<a href=\"https://flic.kr/s/aHsk9CwBC1\">TD on Flickr</a>.</p>"
